These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: juice, tea
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: soul, country
1. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
2. the fan of country is on the right of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2   |
| Beverage   | tea  | juice |
| Music-Genre       | soul | country |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, water
The people have 2 different jobs:  architect, lawyer
1. the lawyer is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
2. the person drinking water is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2   |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | water |
| Job      | lawyer     | architect  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: sports, western
The people have 2 different hobbies: board-games, photography
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | western  |
| Hobby   | board-games | photography |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-4::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: amber, turquise
There 2 different types of food: apricot, tomato
1. the person eating apricot is on the right of the person who likes turquise##1
2. the person who likes amber is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |
| Color   | turquise | amber   |
| Food       | tomato | apricot |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-5::.
