The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, train
1. the person driving the train is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
2. the fan of salsa is on the left or right of the fan of ambient##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |
| Music-Genre   | salsa    | ambient    |
| Transport   | bus | train |

