.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-7::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: july, december
2 different pets are kept: cat, snake
1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in july##3
2. the owner of the snake is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |  2   |
| Birthday   | july | december |
| Pet           | snake     | cat  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-8::.
City: boston, new-york
The people have 2 different jobs:  chef, manager
1. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
2. the manager is on the left or right of the person traveling to new-york##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |
| City   | new-york | boston |
| Job     | chef        | manager |

